    "This chapter introduces machine learning and its privacy definitions and threats, summarizes the current situation in the field of privacy protection, analyzes advantages and disadvantages, and looks forward to possible research directions in the future.",
    "Machine learningMachine learning (ML) uses computers to effectively mimic human learning activities.",
    "It learns from existing data and produces useful models to make decisions about future behavior.In traditional machine learning training, the data of all parties is first collected by the data collector, and then the data analyst conducts model training.",
